1
00:01:05,854 --> 00:01:08,286
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,414 --> 00:01:11,326
=Episode 12=

3
00:01:11,959 --> 00:01:13,799
Your disguise isn't clever.

4
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:16,840
Here's some money.

5
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:17,959
You should go.

6
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:27,719
I know the nearby terrain well.

7
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:28,840
I can take you

8
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,439
wherever you want to go.

9
00:01:32,879 --> 00:01:33,640
Take her away.

10
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:34,760
Watch her closely.

11
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:35,799
Yes.

12
00:01:45,439 --> 00:01:45,959
Your Majesty.

13
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:48,319
The marching route is confidential.

14
00:01:48,719 --> 00:01:51,280
Your Majesty, how do you think
the Dada people found out?

15
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,040
There's a traitor.

16
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:56,040
Please send a letter to Xiao...

17
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:57,879
Prince Xiaoyao.

18
00:01:58,280 --> 00:02:00,239
Tell him what has happened
these past two days.

19
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:01,579
Yes.

20
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,040
And...

21
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:07,280
Please do not tell
Xu Yu about the ambush.

22
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:08,960
I don't want her to worry.

23
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:10,360
Yes.

24
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:18,240
The prince comes to Fengyi Palace
every day to review memorials.

25
00:02:18,319 --> 00:02:19,759
It must be that His Majesty ordered

26
00:02:19,759 --> 00:02:21,360
the Empress to guide him.

27
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:24,080
Aunt, you must have misunderstood.

28
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:29,080
What memorials require Xu Yu's guidance?

29
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,879
Is the Xu family trying to seize power?

30
00:02:30,879 --> 00:02:32,439
Or are they trying to corrupt Jinming?

31
00:02:32,759 --> 00:02:35,800
Aunt, please do not listen to
the slander of petty people.

32
00:02:37,639 --> 00:02:40,280
Look, isn't the prince
reviewing memorials?

33
00:02:42,719 --> 00:02:43,879
This should be like this.

34
00:02:51,719 --> 00:02:53,240
Such a deep bond as in-laws.

35
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:55,080
They are only admiring flowers and art.

36
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:56,759
Just some elegant pastimes.

37
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:59,039
Summon Xu Yu to Ci'an Palace.

38
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:01,919
Yes.

39
00:03:03,070 --> 00:03:05,280
(Ci'an Palace)

40
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,879
Mother.

41
00:03:08,759 --> 00:03:09,520
Kneel down.

42
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:12,560
Have I done something wrong?

43
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,159
Kneel down now!

44
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:21,680
I thought your family
had upright values.

45
00:03:22,039 --> 00:03:24,599
I never expected you
to commit such disgraceful acts.

46
00:03:24,879 --> 00:03:25,800
Disgraceful acts?

47
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:28,840
Jinyun is fighting on the battlefield.

48
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,639
Instead of sharing his burdens,

49
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,400
you have an affair with Jinming.

50
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,039
What?

51
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:36,960
Mother, I can explain.

52
00:03:37,159 --> 00:03:37,919
Someone!

53
00:03:48,439 --> 00:03:49,400
(She is)

54
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:50,919
(going to kill me?)

55
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,080
Xu Yu.

56
00:03:53,439 --> 00:03:53,960
Mother.

57
00:03:54,759 --> 00:03:58,199
Do you remember what His Majesty
said to you before his departure?

58
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,039
I also hope that

59
00:04:01,439 --> 00:04:04,400
Xu Yu won't get hurt
under any circumstances.

60
00:04:04,919 --> 00:04:08,240
Whatever happens,
await my return for final judgment.

61
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:15,080
You are the Empress.

62
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,639
I will not kill you for now.

63
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:20,680
But from today onward,
you're not to step out of Fengyi Palace.

64
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:21,800
Mother.

65
00:04:22,439 --> 00:04:25,160
Before His Majesty's departure,
he instructed me

66
00:04:25,519 --> 00:04:27,360
to supervise the prince
in court affairs.

67
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:30,319
Today, the prince didn't want
to attend the matchmaking at the garden,

68
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:32,360
so he asked me to come and persuade you.

69
00:04:32,879 --> 00:04:35,240
But unexpectedly, you didn't appear.

70
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:36,800
Someone!

71
00:04:40,759 --> 00:04:42,360
Summon Jinming to Ci'an Palace.

72
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:43,759
Yes.

73
00:04:45,839 --> 00:04:46,680
Empress Dowager.

74
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,839
The Third Prince has arrived.

75
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,560
It's a trap.

76
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,079
Who is spreading rumors about me,

77
00:04:56,079 --> 00:04:57,600
saying I go to Fengyi Palace daily?

78
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,160
It must be that upstart.

79
00:04:59,519 --> 00:05:00,160
Who is it?

80
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,120
Consort Zhao.

81
00:05:02,519 --> 00:05:04,480
He wears gold and silver daily.

82
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:07,399
He's annoyed that Consort Zhao

83
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:10,319
looks more extravagant than him.

84
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,959
But Your Highness, I must remind you.

85
00:05:13,879 --> 00:05:16,600
Now, Prince Ning
has gone to Ci'an Palace too.

86
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,279
My uncle has gone too?

87
00:05:18,519 --> 00:05:19,680
Won't that make things worse?

88
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:20,680
Not only that.

89
00:05:21,399 --> 00:05:22,879
He'll surely make false accusations,

90
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,720
saying you two have an affair.

91
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:28,319
What are you doing?

92
00:05:28,839 --> 00:05:30,000
Going to Ci'an Palace

93
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:30,959
to poison them all.

94
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:31,839
Are you insane?

95
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:33,240
Where are you going?

96
00:05:33,879 --> 00:05:34,759
Going to Ci'an Palace

97
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:37,319
to see if you can think of an idea

98
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:39,079
to rescue the Empress.

99
00:05:39,079 --> 00:05:40,319
Think of an idea?

100
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:42,639
What if I can't?

101
00:05:43,279 --> 00:05:44,480
Then poison them all.

102
00:05:44,839 --> 00:05:45,639
Terrible idea.

103
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:46,800
All terrible ideas.

104
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,160
- Going or not?
- Going or not?

105
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,040
I'm not going to be a coward.

106
00:06:05,079 --> 00:06:05,720
Empress Dowager.

107
00:06:06,199 --> 00:06:08,680
Today, I heard a palace rumor

108
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:10,000
about the Empress,

109
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,279
so I came to verify it.

110
00:06:11,279 --> 00:06:14,560
Now, it seems the Empress
has indeed acted improperly.

111
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:17,439
The palace has its own rules.

112
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:19,160
It's not your place to interfere.

113
00:06:20,399 --> 00:06:22,759
I am His Majesty's uncle after all.

114
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:26,000
It's my duty to purify the palace.

115
00:06:26,439 --> 00:06:29,600
Otherwise, if this rumor spreads out...

116
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,319
Enough!

117
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,160
Mother!

118
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,000
Mother.

119
00:06:36,959 --> 00:06:37,480
Mother.

120
00:06:37,759 --> 00:06:38,360
There's a way.

121
00:06:38,879 --> 00:06:40,519
The Grand Preceptor invites the consorts

122
00:06:40,759 --> 00:06:42,079
to the imperial garden to pray

123
00:06:42,079 --> 00:06:43,040
for repelling exorcism.

124
00:06:44,199 --> 00:06:45,639
The Empress will suffer no more.

125
00:06:48,879 --> 00:06:49,399
Here.

126
00:06:58,399 --> 00:06:59,319
It's time.

127
00:06:59,959 --> 00:07:00,759
Physician Jiang.

128
00:07:01,319 --> 00:07:01,839
Please.

129
00:07:19,079 --> 00:07:20,120
What's this?

130
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:22,439
Lately, the Empress
has been speaking improperly

131
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:24,399
because she's lovesick for His Majesty.

132
00:07:25,439 --> 00:07:26,639
Evil spirits have entered her.

133
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:29,480
I have a way to cure it.

134
00:07:34,639 --> 00:07:36,720
(What are they doing now?)

135
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,279
Uncle.

136
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:44,439
My sister-in-law even burned
Mother's favorite painting.

137
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,079
If this gets out,

138
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:47,519
the royal dignity will be lost.

139
00:07:47,879 --> 00:07:50,560
Besides, you won't be able
to hold your head up.

140
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,439
Isn't that right?

141
00:07:52,199 --> 00:07:52,839
Your Highness.

142
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:56,160
You're close kin and highly respected.

143
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:58,560
I have an impertinent request.

144
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:01,519
May I use your blood
as a medicinal catalyst?

145
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:03,720
You won't refuse, will you?

146
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,560
Of course my uncle won't refuse.

147
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:08,040
He cares most for us juniors.

148
00:08:08,399 --> 00:08:09,240
Isn't that so?

149
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,920
Please follow me.

150
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:24,899
Your Highness, please.

151
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:37,200
Close the door.

152
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:44,360
Even if you sent your uncle away,

153
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:46,120
must you make your scandal
in Fengyi Palace

154
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,600
known to all?

155
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:48,600
Mother.

156
00:08:49,279 --> 00:08:52,120
Let the prince tell you
why he came to Fengyi Palace.

157
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:53,320
Mother.

158
00:08:54,159 --> 00:08:55,600
Didn't you tell me to go

159
00:08:55,879 --> 00:08:57,679
to Fengyi Palace to discuss my marriage?

160
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:59,519
But I don't want to marry.

161
00:08:59,799 --> 00:09:01,120
So I asked her to persuade you.

162
00:09:01,879 --> 00:09:02,840
If she succeeded,

163
00:09:03,159 --> 00:09:05,000
I'd review memorials
in the study every day.

164
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:09,080
When did I tell you
to discuss marriage with her?

165
00:09:09,559 --> 00:09:13,440
Didn't she make you
review memorials in Fengyi Palace?

166
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:19,320
Where is Zhao Qiluo?

167
00:09:19,519 --> 00:09:20,120
I know.

168
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,799
She's praying in the garden.

169
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:23,039
Summon her inside.

170
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,159
Aunt.

171
00:09:44,759 --> 00:09:45,519
Zhao Qiluo.

172
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:48,840
Didn't Lady Tao teach you
a harsh lesson?

173
00:09:55,519 --> 00:09:56,639
Aunt, please calm down.

174
00:09:57,720 --> 00:10:01,399
I did send someone
to deliver a message to the prince.

175
00:10:01,399 --> 00:10:03,639
But I did it all for His Majesty.

176
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:06,919
That day, I clearly saw
them acting intimately.

177
00:10:07,519 --> 00:10:09,080
That's why I resorted to this plan.

178
00:10:09,559 --> 00:10:12,759
It was only due to
my concern for His Majesty.

179
00:10:12,759 --> 00:10:14,120
I beg for your mercy.

180
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:18,639
You slandered me and the regent prince.

181
00:10:18,639 --> 00:10:19,679
This is a grave offense.

182
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,679
You also forged a decree.

183
00:10:22,879 --> 00:10:24,200
That makes the crime even worse.

184
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:26,200
Xu Yu.

185
00:10:32,519 --> 00:10:33,519
Aunt.

186
00:10:37,879 --> 00:10:41,080
From today, you're stripped
of your Noble Consort title.

187
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,200
Demoted to Virtuous Consort.

188
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:44,240
You're confined for three months.

189
00:11:03,519 --> 00:11:04,120
Your Highness.

190
00:11:04,759 --> 00:11:06,919
You faced suspicion
of intimacy with His Majesty.

191
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,639
How can you be so happy now?

192
00:11:09,759 --> 00:11:10,879
You don't understand.

193
00:11:11,559 --> 00:11:12,759
Though we were misunderstood,

194
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:16,240
I won't have to review memorials
with Jinyun anymore.

195
00:11:16,639 --> 00:11:19,639
Do you think avoiding me
means escaping memorial duty?

196
00:11:19,879 --> 00:11:20,679
Jinyun.

197
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,600
Jinyun, why are you here?

198
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,279
No, you must leave!

199
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:26,399
We can't be seen together again.

200
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,879
Isn't the Grand Preceptor here?

201
00:11:29,759 --> 00:11:30,259
Take a seat.

202
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:36,159
Good idea.

203
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:40,000
This way, we won't be misunderstood.

204
00:11:41,279 --> 00:11:42,679
That is enough.

205
00:11:43,399 --> 00:11:44,440
Your Majesty,

206
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:46,919
did you come to have me
divine the Empress's safety?

207
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:47,759
Right.

208
00:11:48,799 --> 00:11:49,879
I read the battle report.

209
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:52,360
She was ambushed
immediately after setting out.

210
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:54,919
It's likely an inside job.

211
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:56,679
I can't stop worrying.

212
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:57,840
Is she alright?

213
00:11:58,720 --> 00:11:59,320
She's fine.

214
00:12:13,632 --> 00:12:14,656
(Danger)

215
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:17,840
What's wrong?

216
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,080
How is Xu Yu?

217
00:12:19,279 --> 00:12:19,919
Your Majesty.

218
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:20,500
Not good.

219
00:12:20,919 --> 00:12:23,519
The divination shows
Her Majesty will face grave peril.

220
00:12:23,519 --> 00:12:24,320
What?

221
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:30,840
Leading the charge,

222
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:32,720
storming the battlefield,

223
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,559
and repelling enemies.

224
00:12:36,120 --> 00:12:38,440
Is this useless Xiao Jinyun?

225
00:12:38,919 --> 00:12:42,240
Defeating you at archery last time
could be considered as luck.

226
00:12:43,399 --> 00:12:45,679
But now, he's become so fiercely brave.

227
00:12:48,559 --> 00:12:50,360
Since the Xunfang Pavilion
was destroyed,

228
00:12:50,879 --> 00:12:53,679
your remaining people
have become increasingly useless.

229
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,720
After investigating
Xiao Jinyun for long,

230
00:12:55,720 --> 00:12:58,399
you still can't tell me
why he's become a different man.

231
00:12:59,159 --> 00:13:02,120
Could there truly be
a mystical soul-exchange?

232
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:04,120
Can someone really change?

233
00:13:04,679 --> 00:13:05,840
What are you implying?

234
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:08,240
Like Xiao Jinyun and Xu Yu

235
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:10,000
have their souls swapped?

236
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:12,960
I don't believe in such heresy.

237
00:13:14,039 --> 00:13:16,200
But there's one thing we must do now.

238
00:13:16,639 --> 00:13:18,559
Time to put the pressure on Dada.

239
00:13:19,399 --> 00:13:20,736
Have them exhaust Xiao Jinyun

240
00:13:21,824 --> 00:13:23,879
in the desert until he dies.

241
00:13:25,639 --> 00:13:26,279
Alright.

242
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:32,279
(Let's observe Dada's probing results.)

243
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:35,120
(If Xiao Jinyun survives again,)

244
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:39,840
(then this astonishing wonder
will be true.)

245
00:13:58,679 --> 00:13:59,600
Yu.

246
00:14:26,247 --> 00:14:31,431
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

247
00:14:32,167 --> 00:14:36,730
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

248
00:14:38,055 --> 00:14:43,470
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

249
00:14:44,039 --> 00:14:48,583
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

250
00:14:49,223 --> 00:14:54,487
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

251
00:14:54,855 --> 00:15:00,532
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

252
00:15:00,871 --> 00:15:02,887
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

253
00:15:03,079 --> 00:15:06,823
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

254
00:15:07,399 --> 00:15:12,071
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

255
00:15:12,615 --> 00:15:14,375
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

256
00:15:14,695 --> 00:15:18,311
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

257
00:15:18,558 --> 00:15:24,085
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪
